<h1 class="display-4">輕軌運量查詢 (快速搜尋)</h1>

<p>您可以在此輸入年份與月份進行查詢，按下「查詢」會轉到輕軌資料管理頁顯示結果。</p>

<form asp-controller="Rail" asp-action="Index" method="get" class="mb-3">
    <div class="row g-3 align-items-center">
        <div class="col-auto">
            <label class="col-form-label">年份：</label>
        </div>
        <div class="col-auto">
            <input type="text" name="searchYear" class="form-control" placeholder="輸入民國年 (如:113)">
        </div>

        <div class="col-auto">
            <label class="col-form-label">月份：</label>
        </div>
        <div class="col-auto">
            <input type="text" name="searchMonth" class="form-control" placeholder="輸入月份">
        </div>

        <div class="col-auto">
            <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary">查詢</button>
            <a asp-controller="Rail" asp-action="Index" asp-route-showAll="true" class="btn btn-outline-secondary">管理頁顯示全部</a>
        </div>
    </div>
</form>

<div class="text-center mt-4">
    <p>或者使用上方導覽連結進入「輕軌資料管理」頁面以查看全部資料。</p>
